solutions.title: Extract Data from Documents using DocAl
solutions.description: This architecture uses Google Document Al to extract document data, storing it in BigOuery. It automates tasks like invoice processing, contract analysis, and document classification.

solutions.title: Edit Images using Imagen
solutions.description: Deploy Google Cloud Imagen API to auto-mask images and edit them based on your prompts

solutions.title: Indentify Objects in Images
solutions.description: Deploy Google Cloud Vision API to detect objects in images, save results as JSON, and import to BigOuery. Supports visual search, content moderation, and inventory management.

solutions.title: Sentiment Analysis(Coming soon)
solutions.description: Automates sentiment analysis with the Natural Language API, storing results in Cloud Storage and BigOuery. It supports feedback, brand monitoring, research, social media, and engagement.

solutions.title: Classify Keywords with Al(Coming soon)
solutions.description: Uses GenAl to classify texts, store results in BigQuery, and visualize them in Looker Studio for organizing documents, tagging products, prioritizing tickets, aiding diagnoses, and detecting plagiarism.
